data.text: @StylishSoprano Yeah, i zonked out early yesterday but otherwise fine.
@MargarGuitar Super sore arm and tired for a few days. Mostly fine! Are you okay?
@StylishSoprano How did you end up doing afterward? How do you feel today?

@StylishSoprano Moderna shot 2 day 2- woke up feeling like I had the flu. Hot, chills tired  nose stuffed up. Tried to do some remote work deadlines for a couple of hours. Slept all day. Now afraid to look at work e-mail. Think “I feel like I have the flu” is going to be my catch phrase this wk.

@StylishSoprano I had a sore arm, and minor headache/nausea with shot 2! I was tired but nothing a nap couldn’t fix! My bf got it too and we went to Best Buy that evening to pick up my AC Switch (that he dropped and is now scratched and chipped!😭)
@MargarGuitar Good call!!! I’m gonna do that too! The flu shot usually pummels me for a day or so. I’m expecting something similar in a few weeks when I go for 2.

@StylishSoprano I just got home from my second vaccine! Popped a tylenol preemptively because an acquaintance reported severe headache and tiredness. I have to work at 1pm so fingers crossed!!
Good luck to you! All I haf was a tolerably sore arm for my first shot. Also Pfizer.
